# HMS Patient Registration — Environment Variables

| Variable | Description | Example |
|----------|-------------|---------|
| `PORT` | HTTP listen port | `8080` |
| `ASPNETCORE_ENVIRONMENT` | Environment name | `Production` |
| `DataMode` | `Mock` or `SqlServer` | `Mock` |
| `ConnectionStrings__DefaultConnection` | SQL Server connection | `Server=...` |
| `Security__RequireAuth` | Enforce JWT on protected endpoints | `false` |
| `Security__EnableSwagger` | Enable Swagger UI | `true` |
| `Jwt__Key` | JWT signing key (min 32 chars) | `your-secret-key` |
| `Jwt__Issuer` | Token issuer | `HMS.PatientRegistration` |
| `Jwt__Audience` | Token audience | `HMS.Client` |
| `Cors__AllowedOrigins__0` | Allowed CORS origin | `https://app.example.com` |

